original_title: Lisa Stansfield - Live at Ronnie Scott's
overview: Recorded during a sell-out week at the world famous Ronnie Scott's jazz club, in the heart of London's Soho. Here is a showcase for many of her greatest hits, along with renditions of some of the outstanding jazz tunes of all time.
